            <div><h2><b>🎉 Cross Culture 特色中文课 正式招生啦！🎉</b></h2></div>
            <div><h3>沉浸式中文教学+文化艺术交流 = 独一无二的中文学习体验</h3></div>
            <div class="text-muted" style="font-size: 20px;">
Canadian Chinese Cross Culture Club(4Cclub) 是一个推动和促进中国文化融入加拿大多元文化以及加中文化艺术交流的非盈利组织。我们提供的课程不仅仅是简单的中文课，而是全景式、沉浸式的中国文化、艺术和历史的学习和体验。
<br/><br/>
●	特色中文课面向没有中文环境和基础的学生学习中文口语（听说）、提供零基础，初中级中文口语班，读写班等。<br/>
●	书法、中国乐器、戏曲、舞蹈等各种不同形式的中国传统文化艺术家现场展示和指导。<br/>
●	邀请加拿大著名的中国历史学者、作家、科学工作者、行业专家前来做专题讲座。<br/>
●	每年我们还组织学生赴中国的游学和交流活动，加深对中国文化的了解。并可根据学生的实际情况和需要推荐到中国大学学习。
            </div>
            <hr>
            
            <div><h2><b>Cross Culture Special Chinese Program – Now Open for Enrollment!</b></h2></div>
            <div><h3>Immersive Chinese Language + Cultural Arts Exchange = A Unique Chinese Learning Experience</h3></div>
            <div class="text-muted" style="font-size: 20px;">
The Canadian Chinese Cross Culture Club(4Cclub) is a non-profit organization dedicated to promoting and integrating Chinese culture into Canada's multicultural landscape and fostering Sino-Canadian cultural and artistic exchange.
<br/><br/>
We offer more than just Chinese classes — our programs provide a panoramic, immersive experience in Chinese language, arts, and history.
<br/><br/>
🌱 Our Special Chinese Program is designed for learners with no Chinese environment or background. We offer beginner and intermediate Chinese speaking (listening/speaking) and reading/writing classes.<br/>
🖌️ We invite artists in calligraphy, traditional Chinese instruments, opera, and dance to give live demonstrations and hands-on instruction.<br/>
📚 Renowned Canadian historians, writers, scientists, and industry experts are regularly invited to deliver in-depth lectures on Chinese culture and topics of interest.<br/>
✈️ Every year, we organize study tours and cultural exchange programs to China, deepening students' understanding of Chinese culture. We can also provide recommendations to Chinese universities based on individual needs and academic goals.
            </div>           
